     Curr. Biol. 13:405-410(2003).
     PubMed=12620189
[ 4] Setty S.R., Shin M.E., Yoshino A., Marks M.S., Burd C.G.
     "Golgi recruitment of GRIP domain proteins by Arf-like GTPase 1 is
     regulated by Arf-like GTPase 3."
     Curr. Biol. 13:401-404(2003).
     PubMed=12620188

